Go in peace to love and serve the Lord.

7
00:00:54.472 --> 00:00:57.391
Thanks be to God.

8
00:01:05.775 --> 00:01:07.860
Good morning, Mary. How are you?

9
00:01:09.487 --> 00:01:11.822
Good morning, Elizabeth. How are you?

10
00:01:11.906 --> 00:01:13.783
Good morning, Bernie.

11
00:01:13.866 --> 00:01:17.244
Father, would you say a prayer
to Our Lady for an intervention?

12
00:01:17.328 --> 00:01:19.455
- What's wrong? Is someone sick?
- No.

13
00:01:19.538 --> 00:01:23.334
